               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18411129-name-1317" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1317" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1317" type="surname" value="DRAPER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18411129-name-1317" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN DRAPER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a plumber, living at Hounslow. On the 20th of November, I went to my melting shop—I found the window broken, which led me to suspect the place had been entered—I missed half a cwt. of old lead which had been left in my shop—I informed the police-man —the lead now produced is mine—it was brought to me by Waters on the Tuesday following, the 23rd—he asked me if I would buy some lead—I found it belonged to me, end the officer took him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PRENDEROAST</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Half a cwt. is rather heavy for inch a lad as Curtis to carry? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes.</p>
