                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant T</hi> 20.) I received information on the 23rd of November, that the lead had been offered at the prosecutor's house, I took Curtis into custody on the 20th—I saw some footsteps—I compared them with Curtis's—I took him on suspicion.</p>
